      <title>分析师称美联储降息利好亚洲股市和风险货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-positive-for-asian-stocks-risk-currencies-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，美联储决定将基准利率下调 50 个基点，这可能对亚洲股市产生积极影响，因为这为该地区的央行放松政策提供了更多空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-positive-for-asian-stocks-risk-currencies-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
